com.qapel.rfid.controller

Class ReaderConfigurationController

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.qapel.rfid.controller.ReaderConfigurationController

  • @Controller
 @RequestMapping(value="/readerConfiguration/")
public class ReaderConfigurationController
extends java.lang.Object
    Controller for handling reader configuration (stations table in db) This controller uses the JBA model for data base access using ReaderConfiguration and Station entities This controller is set up as a Thymeleaf template, each call populates a template and returns the template for display. Some calls perform additional db actions
